    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept, and ready to enjoy, this is a good honest car that presents nicely and should make its next owner very happy. It shows well overall with the light cosmetic and age-related wear you\u2019d expect from a well-cared-for driver, and it offers a strong balance of appearance, usability, and value. A solid example for someone looking for a car they can enjoy right away without pretending it\u2019s perfect.",
