    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Honest project-grade vehicle in poor overall condition. It appears largely complete, but it shows significant age, wear, and neglect throughout. Expect heavy cosmetic flaws, tired paint and trim, and an interior that will need a thorough cleaning and likely refurbishment. Buyers should plan on mechanical sorting, deferred maintenance, and repairs before regular use. Best suited for someone looking for a budget project, parts car, or restoration candidate rather than a turn-key driver.",
