    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$33,900 - Good-condition example that presents well overall and appears to have been cared for. The paint, body, and interior all show nicely, with normal age-appropriate wear and some minor cosmetic imperfections you would expect from a used vehicle, but nothing that takes away from it as a clean, enjoyable driver. It should appeal to buyers looking for a well-kept car they can use and enjoy right away, while understanding it is not a flawless showpiece.",
