    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-minded option with plenty of potential for someone seeking dependable basic use, a project car, or an inexpensive second vehicle. A straightforward opportunity to own at a highly accessible price point.",
